The collection of very high heels, modeled by the former reality star herself, includes a pair of jewel-encrusted stilettos inspired by a vintage Victorian necklace she owns.

Saks Fifth Avenue will stock the fall collection from September, as will Lane Crawford, Tsum and Holt Renfrew; while Net-A-Porter will be the only online retailer to sell them.

