Last month, she designed a capsule collection of sunglasses for Westward Leaning, retailing for $210 a pair.

'No other person... has the kind of conversion power that Olivia has,' Westward Leaning's co-founder Robert Denning said in June. 'When Justin Bieber and Selena Gomez broke up, he left wearing the pair of sunglasses we’d gifted Selena.

'I thought it would lead to a huge spike in sales, but didn’t move the dial at all.'

If her apparent Midas touch with Westward Leaning's wares is anything to go by, Ms Palmero's Aquazzura collaboration is likely to be a storming success.

